Bick]], science fiction writer * [[Ilsa Konrads]] (born 1944), Australian freestyle swimmer ==Fiction== * [[Ilsa (novel)|''Ilsa'' (novel)]], a 1946 novel by Madeleine L'Engle * ''[[Ilsa, She Wolf of the SS]]'', a 1975 Nazi exploitation film * ''[[Ilsa, Harem Keeper of the Oil Sheiks]]'', a 1976 sexploitation film * ''[[Ilsa, the Tigress of Siberia]]'', a 1977 sexploitation film ===Fictional characters=== * Ilsa Lund, in the 1942 film [[Casablanca (film)|''Casablanca'']] * [[Human Target (2010 TV series)#Main characters|Ilsa Pucci]], from the TV series ''Human Target'' * [[List of recurring characters in The Suite Life of Zack & Cody#Other characters|Ilsa Shickelgrubermeiger]], from the TV series ''The Suite Life of Zack and Cody'' ==Other== * [[Tropical Storm Ilsa (disambiguation)]], various cyclones * [[International Law Students Association]], a non-profit association of students and lawyers dedicated to the promotion of international law * [[Interstate Land Sales Full Disclosure Act of 1968]], US Congressional act passed to facilitate regulation of interstate land sales * [[Iran and Libya Sanctions Act]], a 1996 act of the US Congress that imposed economic sanctions on firms doing business with Iran and Libya ==See also== * [[Ilse (disambiguation)]] {{disambiguation|given name}}
